 \"from\": 1802, \"to\": 1943, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some intense battles\", \"from\": 1833, \"to\": 1853}, {\"ngram\": \"the next couple\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 1874}, {\"ngram\": \"weeks\", \"from\": 1878, \"to\": 1883}, {\"ngram\": \"the British Championships\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 1920}, {\"ngram\": \"then the Olympics\", \"from\": 1925, \"to\": 1942}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can guarantee right now there are going to be medals for the UK at the Olympic Games in the 1500 and they can come from any one of us.\\\"\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 2083, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2009, \"end\": 2011, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999377510013, \"rank\": 4.26418117772327e-08, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2000}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2015, \"to\": 2032}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2079, \"to\": 2081}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kerr ran a personal-best time of 3:29.05 at the Tokyo Games to take Olympic bronze behind Ingebrigtsen and Kenya's Timothy Cheruiyot but has since raised his level to become arguably the best 1500m runner in the world.\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2303, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2192, \"end\": 2197, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 0.9973880069021139, \"rank\": 0.0026182847458986963, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}, {\"begin\": 2200, \"end\": 2217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Timothy_Cheruiyot\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Timothy Cheruiyot\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Timothy_Cheruiyot\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Timothy_Cheruiyot\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kerr\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2089}, {\"ngram\": \"a personal-best time\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2114}, {\"ngram\": \"3:29.05\", \"from\": 2118, \"to\": 2125}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Games\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2144}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic bronze\", \"from\": 2153, \"to\": 2167}, {\"ngram\": \"Ingebrigtsen\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2187}, {\"ngram\": \"his level\", \"from\": 2239, \"to\": 2248}, {\"ngram\": \"the best 1500m runner\", \"from\": 2268, \"to\": 2289}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2302}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He believes Mo Farah's British 1500m record time of 3:28.81 is in his sights and hopes that his Eugene victory \\\"showed my form to the British selectors\\\", enabling him to run the 800m at the Olympic trials in July to work on his speed.\", \"from\": 2305, \"to\": 2539, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2439, \"end\": 2446, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9467643272316506, \"rank\": 0.04898901036983135, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"1500m\", \"from\": 2336, \"to\": 2341}, {\"ngram\": \"3:28.81\", \"from\": 2357, \"to\": 2364}, {\"ngram\": \"his sights\", \"from\": 2371, \"to\": 2381}, {\"ngram\": \"his Eugene victory\", \"from\": 2397, \"to\": 2415}, {\"ngram\": \"my form\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2431}, {\"ngram\": \"the 800m\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2487}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic trials\", \"from\": 2491, \"to\": 2509}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 2513, \"to\": 2517}, {\"ngram\": \"his speed\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2538}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, he is not currently planning to double up and run both distances in Paris, with 1500m still the focus.\", \"from\": 2540, \"to\": 2651, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2617, \"end\": 2622,